      "text": "They can't do it.",
      "start": 508.22,
      "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
      "text": "Real Madrid with Bayern, with City, in the",
      "start": 509.5,
      "duration": 3.299
    },
    {
      "text": "Champions League, they can't do it in Italy,",
      "start": 512.799,
      "duration": 4.961
    },
    {
      "text": "while they're playing in their grandfather's cup.",
      "start": 518.5,
      "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
      "text": "That's how life goes.",
      "start": 521.84,
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "text": "And switching a bit to Arsenal, I saw",
      "start": 524.84,
      "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
      "text": "the most beautiful play in the first half,",
      "start": 530.0,
      "duration": 0.94
    },
    {
      "text": "first of all.",
      "start": 531.04,
      "duration": 0.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Diomande for Araujo, the winger.",
      "start": 531.94,
      "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
      "text": "And Araujo, who takes the cross.",
      "start": 536.88,
      "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
      "text": "A beautiful play.",
      "start": 538.84,
      "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
      "text": "It was a game, I repeat, that wasn't",
      "start": 540.56,
      "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
      "text": "too much.",
      "start": 544.76,
      "duration": 0.82
    },
    {
      "text": "In my opinion, it's Arsenal, among other things,",
      "start": 546.1,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": "that doesn't allow you...",
      "start": 549.26,
      "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
      "text": "I think it's a very Italian team, in",
      "start": 550.82,
      "duration": 4.44
    },
    {
      "text": "many ways, with obviously more quality.",
      "start": 555.26,
      "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
      "text": "With obviously more quality.",
      "start": 558.52,
      "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
      "text": "But that allows me to say that there's",
      "start": 560.52,
      "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
      "text": "no team that can go all the way",
      "start": 562.36,
      "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
      "text": "and win the competition.",
      "start": 564.32,
      "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Even though they're there to win the Premier",
      "start": 565.96,
      "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
      "text": "League.\nIt's not that we're talking about a team,",
      "start": 570.32,
      "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
      "text": "but it doesn't give me the feeling of",
      "start": 572.88,
      "duration": 3.82
    },
    {
      "text": "power that I feel when I see Bayern,",
      "start": 576.7,
      "duration": 6.36
    },
    {
      "text": "Barcelona and the singing company.",
      "start": 583.2,
      "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 587.82,
      "duration": 0.6
    },
    {
      "text": "PSG.",
      "start": 588.6,
      "duration": 0.56
    },
    {
      "text": "PSG, as we call them.",
      "start": 589.38,
      "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 592.92,
      "duration": 0.62
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see a bit.",
      "start": 594.2,
      "duration": 0.86
    },
    {
      "text": "The fact is that today there's also a",
      "start": 595.38,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
      "text": "certain mortgage, because in my opinion he had",
      "start": 598.14,
      "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
      "text": "also studied it a bit to play it",
      "start": 600.84,
      "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
      "text": "back.",
      "start": 602.84,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "It's true that there were also some absences.",
      "start": 604.0,
      "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
      "text": "Let's think of Saka, what's his name?",
      "start": 607.1,
      "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
      "text": "Eze.",
      "start": 610.36,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "He's a player that I like to die",
      "start": 610.86,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": "for.",
      "start": 614.22,
      "duration": 0.36
    },
    {
      "text": "But the most beautiful things were shown to",
      "start": 614.58,
      "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
      "text": "me by Sporting, as far as I'm concerned.",
      "start": 616.72,
      "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
      "text": "Even at the end of the game, in",
      "start": 618.78,
      "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
      "text": "Katam, he had a couple of situations.",
      "start": 620.52,
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "text": "In my opinion, the game was there.",
      "start": 623.6,
      "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
      "text": "To end in parity, maybe Sporting had a",
      "start": 626.84,
      "duration": 4.3
    },
    {
      "text": "bit more points, but let's say it, at",
      "start": 631.14,
      "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
      "text": "these levels, it's the quality that makes the",
      "start": 634.62,
      "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
      "text": "difference.",
      "start": 637.76,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Martinelli's quality.",
      "start": 639.88,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "I have to say that Martinelli, who came",
      "start": 640.44,
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "text": "on, did a beautiful play.",
      "start": 642.16,
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "text": "The goal for 90% of his time,",
      "start": 644.2,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "text": "then he did a great job.",
      "start": 647.4,
      "duration": 0.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Lavers too, for goodness' sake.",
      "start": 648.26,
      "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "start": 649.64,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "But the crucial play was scored by Martinelli.",
      "start": 651.26,
      "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Sporting did it in this competition.",
      "start": 658.84,
      "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
      "text": "I don't see Sporting so far from the",
      "start": 665.62,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": "level of Italian football.",
      "start": 668.94,
      "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 675.62,
      "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 677.44,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "It's a win.",
      "start": 678.18,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "I think that at home, Arsenal don't have",
      "start": 679.5,
      "duration": 5.18
    },
    {
      "text": "any problems.",
      "start": 684.68,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "They're a tough team.",
      "start": 685.76,
      "duration": 0.92
    },
    {
      "text": "But I have the feeling, I repeat, that",
      "start": 688.86,
      "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
      "text": "they can't get to the bottom.",
      "start": 691.04,
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "text": "They're a bit of a minivagant team.",
      "start": 693.54,
      "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
      "text": "They know how to mess up the opponent's",
      "start": 696.22,
      "duration": 2.42
    },
    {
      "text": "game, as they did last year with Inter,",
      "start": 698.64,
      "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
      "text": "for example, with Bayern.",
      "start": 700.26,
      "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 703.66,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "But today, I'm not going to put them",
      "start": 704.8,
      "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
      "text": "among my favorites.",
      "start": 705.88,
      "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
      "text": "Okay, gentlemen.",
      "start": 709.34,
      "duration": 0.76
    },
    {
      "text": "Let me know what you think.",
      "start": 710.24,
